\plain\itap0\s0\fi0\sb200\sa0\aspalpha\aspnum\adjustright\ltrpar\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\qj\faauto\sl260\slmult0\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24{\rtlch\af2\alang1025\afs24\ltrch\b0\i0\fs20\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\strike0\ulnone\cf2 JONATHAN ALTER: Oh, yeah.}
{\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24\par}\pard\plain\itap0\s0\fi0\sb200\sa0\aspalpha\aspnum\adjustright\ltrpar\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\qj\faauto\sl260\slmult0\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24{\rtlch\af2\alang1025\afs24\ltrch\b0\i0\fs20\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033
\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\strike0\ulnone\cf2 BOB SCHIEFFER: But it was always to a purpose.}{\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24\par}\pard\plain\itap0\s0\fi0\sb200\sa0\aspalpha\aspnum\adjustright\ltrpar\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\qj\faauto\sl260\slmult0\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24{
\rtlch\af2\alang1025\afs24\ltrch\b0\i0\fs20\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\strike0\ulnone\cf2 JONATHAN ALTER: Yes, yes, it was always to a purpose. Sometimes to a self-serving purpose, but a lot of times to something for the country, to get something done, or at least to try to get something done.}
{\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24\par}\pard\plain\itap0\s0\fi0\sb200\sa0\aspalpha\aspnum\adjustright\ltrpar\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\qj\faauto\sl260\slmult0\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24{\rtlch\af2\alang1025\afs24\ltrch\b0\i0\fs20\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033
\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\strike0\ulnone\cf2 But I also think that he -- I`ve tried to boil down leadership, because I got -- the reason I was interested in this book, Bob, was to understand what does leadership feel like, smell like, taste like when you really see it? And I guess what I concluded is that if you really oversimplify it, leadership is vision, communication, execution. And that there are very few people, whether it`s in business, government, the PTA, who excel at all three, and Roosevelt did.}
{\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24\par}\pard\plain\itap0\s0\fi0\sb200\sa0\aspalpha\aspnum\adjustright\ltrpar\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\qj\faauto\sl260\slmult0\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24{\rtlch\af2\alang1025\afs24\ltrch\b0\i0\fs20\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033
