\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\strike0\ulnone\cf2 BOB SCHIEFFER: And again, you have just underlined another thing that I think was such an important part of his leadership, and that was his ability to find just the right example.}{\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24\par}
